          </content>
        </paragraph>
        <level>
          <content>
            <p>The feedback given by respondents, including constructive critique on various aspects, has been fully considered and a comprehensive analysis report is available here. Following the consultation exercise, the proposals for the burial regulations have been reviewed and draft burial regulations revised, where appropriate.</p>
          </content>
        </level>
      </section>
      <section eId="section_28">
        <heading>Business</heading>
        <level>
          <content>
            <p>The team has engaged extensively with various businesses, local authorities, representative trade bodies and third sector organisations.</p>
          </content>
        </level>
        <level>
          <heading>The Burial Regulations Working Group ('BRWG'), first established by the Scottish Government in 2016, made a number of initial recommendations relating to the management of burial grounds. After the pandemic the BRWG was re-formed in December 2021 with an updated and expanded membership list including representatives from:</heading>
          <paragraph>
            <num><span style="color:#333333">•</span></num>
            <content>
              <p><span style="color:#333333">Aberdeenshire Council</span></p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph>
            <num><span style="color:#333333">•</span></num>
            <content>
              <p><span style="color:#333333">Association of Local Government Archaeological Officers UK</span></p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph>
            <num><span style="color:#333333">•</span></num>
            <content>
              <p><span style="color:#333333">City of Edinburgh Council</span></p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph>
            <num><span style="color:#333333">•</span></num>
            <content>
              <p><span style="color:#333333">Comhairle nan Eilean Siar</span></p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph>
            <num><span style="color:#333333">•</span></num>
            <content>
              <p><span style="color:#333333">Commonwealth War Graves Commission (CWGC) </span></p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph>
            <num><span style="color:#333333">•</span></num>
            <content>
              <p><span style="color:#333333">Cruse Bereavement Care Scotland</span></p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph>
            <num><span style="color:#333333">•</span></num>
            <content>
              <p><span style="color:#333333">Edinburgh Crematorium Limited</span></p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph>
            <num><span style="color:#333333">•</span></num>
            <content>
              <p><span style="color:#333333">East Ayrshire Council</span></p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph>
            <num><span style="color:#333333">•</span></num>
            <content>
              <p><span style="color:#333333">Federation of Burial and Cremation Authorities (FBCA)</span></p>
            </content>
          </paragraph>
          <paragraph>
            <num><span style="color:#333333">•</span></num>
